Spring Bank of Nigeria in Talks With India’s ICICI About Recapitalization

-- B y   E m e l e   O n u
-- 
2011-06-14T15:26:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-14/spring-bank-of-nigeria-in-talks-with-india-s-icici-about-recapitalization.html
Spring Bank Plc (SPRINGBK) , a Nigerian lender,
said it is in advanced talks with four investors, including
 ICICI Bank Ltd. (ICICIBC) , India’s second-biggest bank, about a
recapitalization.  Other investors include Cloudleap Partners LCC and CARAM
Capital, Spring Bank said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emele Onu in Johannesburg at 
 eonu1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  